### /api/product API calls

### GET all products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/product HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### GET a product by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/product/102 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### POST to create a product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/product HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "sku": "99999",
    "price": 333.50,
    "name": "Air Jordans",
    "description": "Really awesome shoes",
    "quantity": 5
}

### PUT an update to a product
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/product/102 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "sku": "99999",
    "price": 333.50,
    "name": "Air Jordan",
    "description": "Really awesome shoes",
    "quantity": 5
}

### DELETE a product by id
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/product/102 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json